GenerateGraphQLSchemaMojo - Class in com.graphql_java_generator.mavenplugin
The generateGraphQLSchema goal generates GraphQL schema, based on the source GraphQL schemas.
It can be used to: Generate several GraphQL schema files into one file, for instance with additional schema files that would use the extend GraphQL keyword Reformat the schema file Generate the GraphQL schema with the Relay Connection stuff (Node interface, XxxEdge and XxxConnection types), thanks to the addRelayConnections plugin parameter.
